news.title: Signature Apartments residents meet DDA, demand rent payment
news.para: Amarendra Kumar Rakesh, RWA president, said: "We assured DDA that if they start paying the rent, residents will immediately leave." If DDA does not agree, then RWA will approach a court.

news.title: Chintels India's MD gets bail from CBI court
news.para: The Haryana government subsequently transferred the case to the Central Bureau of Investigation (CBI), which registered an FIR in January this year.

news.title: Adani Group to invest over Rs 1,700 crore to expand cement business in Uttarakhand
news.para: "In the cement sector, we will invest in excess of Rs 1,700 crore to expand Ambuja Cements' existing capacity in Uttarakhand," group director Pranav Adani said said.
